{
  "stem": "2946.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I went to the office and who was sitting there?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Fundle.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He was one of the lawyers who was out of the three lawyers teaching with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I said, Otto, Vera came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Can I put her with me as my fiancee on the-- on the police plate so she would be protected?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "OK, I'll do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the uprising was in Warsaw ghetto, and the-- the Germans said that the Jewish policemen in the Warsaw ghetto were smuggling with the police-- with the Polish police-- smuggling arms into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they disbanded the police in Warsaw ghetto-- the Jewish police-- and every ghetto all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were disbanded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The year was '44, I guess. '44.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all my friends in the police-- all my comrades, you know, buddies-- had a summons, and I didn't get one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I ran up to Otto Fundle, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, Otto, what's going on here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to go with my friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't send you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, no, because your-- your [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Your fiancee is half Jewish and you have to stay with her, and I can't send any half Jews into the transport.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was protected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She saved my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because all these, after the war, only six of us came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Six of the policemen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were all transported and gassed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Whew.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a policeman?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we had a sort of uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what the French policemen look like with the hat?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like a square hat?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what we wore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] We had a-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] Okay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a-- a belt across our-- our midriff, and a-- a-- a piece of a-- a leather strip across the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
